{"tid":386901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【從前今日】兩史丹福博士生創立Google","createTime":"2017-09-04T08:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72306f2059596ad6ae824bcd942c8a7d14d8adc1","tid":386901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142491&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142491%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4e5c6fa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20142491%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170904&h=b1e20827\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20142491&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170904</a><br />\n<br />\n【從前今日】兩史丹福博士生創立Google<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞  <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n1998年的今日，Google由兩名美國史丹福大學博士生創立。<br />\n<br />\n當時Google仍是一間私營公司，其宗旨為「匯整全球資訊，供大眾使用，使人人受惠 」而Google這個名字，源自數學大數單詞「googol 」的錯拼，希望Google可以提供一個優質的搜尋引擎。直到2004年，Google首次公開招股，及後成功上市。"},{"pid":"05f9eb76eaa81cf35843df6e18ff84a1a7c76713","tid":386901,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"HAIL GOOGLE"}]}